---
title: Mild Lamb Biryani with Cucumber Raita & Flaked Almonds
description: Prepare your tastebuds for a magical journey with this hearty lamb biryani. The deep Bengal curry paste infused into the basmati rice is beautifully complemented by a cooling cucumber raita and a scattering of sweet currants. Loaded with these rich tastes of India,  the whole family will be transported to a world of flavour.
